  "body": "The [`CrossChainMessenger`](https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/develop/packages/sdk/src/cross-chain-messenger.ts) from the Optimism SDK [exposes all of the Optimism contracts](https://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/6c9b91dbe83e5f056fe05ea9ae0c9c4d694df8f7/packages/sdk/src/cross-chain-messenger.ts#L57) as an object connected to the messenger class. These objects will be connected to the signers or providers passed as inputs to the constructor of the `CrossChainMessenger`. For example, you can get a reference to the `CanonicalTransactionChain` as follows:\r\n\r\n```\r\nconst messenger = new CrossChainMessenger({ ... })\r\nconst ctc = messenger.contracts.l1.CanonicalTransactionChain\r\n```\r\n\r\nSince these contracts can be accessed via the messenger, there's no reason to also have them attached directly to the `OptimismEnv` that gets used in the integration tests:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/6c9b91dbe83e5f056fe05ea9ae0c9c4d694df8f7/integration-tests/test/shared/env.ts#L33-L46\r\n\r\nThe goal of this issue is to remove all references to the contracts as attached to the `OptimismEnv` directly and instead use the reference from the `messenger` attached to the env. For instance, take this line of code:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/6c9b91dbe83e5f056fe05ea9ae0c9c4d694df8f7/integration-tests/test/fee-payment.spec.ts#L12\r\n\r\nThis should be replaced with:\r\n\r\n```\r\nconst gasPrice = await env.messenger.contracts.l1.OVM_GasPriceOracle.setGasPrice(value)\r\n```\r\n\r\nSimilarly, see this line of code:\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/6c9b91dbe83e5f056fe05ea9ae0c9c4d694df8f7/integration-tests/test/fee-payment.spec.ts#L164-L166\r\n\r\nThis should be replaced with:\r\n\r\n```\r\nconst vaultBalance = await env.messenger.contracts.l2.OVM_ETH.balanceOf(\r\n  env.messenger.contracts.l2.OVM_SequencerFeeVault.address\r\n)\r\n```\r\n\r\nSee here for a list of available contracts: \r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/ethereum-optimism/optimism/blob/6c9b91dbe83e5f056fe05ea9ae0c9c4d694df8f7/packages/sdk/src/interfaces/types.ts#L12-L46\r\n",
